<note n="0508002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0508002">愧＝漸【三】</note>
<note n="0508003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0508003">辯＝辦【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0508004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0508004">心＝念【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0508005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0508005">一切施 sarva-dāna</note>
<note n="0508006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0508006">法施 dharma-dāna</note>
<note n="0508007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0508007">財施 āmiṣa-</note>
<note n="0508008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0508008">無畏施 abhaya-</note>
<note n="0509001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0509001">慧＝惠【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0509002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0509002">施障 dāna-vivandha</note>
<note n="0509003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0509003">能對治智 pratipakṣa-jñāna</note>
<note n="0509004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0509004">〔慧〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0509005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0509005">難行施 duskara-dāna</note>
<note n="0509006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0509006">愛＝受【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0509007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0509007">一切門施 sarvato mukhaṁ dānam</note>
<note n="0509008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0509008">善士施 sat-purusa-dāna</note>
<note n="0509009" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0509009">一切種施 Sarvākāraṃ dānaṁ</note>
<note n="0509010" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0509010">一切種施十三相；無依施 aniśrita-dāna, 廣　施 viṣada-(?), 歡喜施 pramudita-, 數數施 abhīkṣna-, 田器施 asānu-(?), 非田施 pātra-(?), 一切物施 Sarva-, 一切處施 Sarvatra-, 一切時施 Sarva- āla-, 無罪施 anavadya-, 有情施 Sarvavastu-, 方土物施 Seśavastu-, 財穀物施 dhana-dhānyavastu-.</note>
<note n="0509011" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0509011">遂求施 vighātarthikaṁ dānam(?)</note>
<note n="0510001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0510001">此世他世樂施 ihāmutra-sukhaṁ dānam</note>
<note n="0510002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0510002">〔此〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0510003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0510003">清淨施 viśuddhaṁdānam.</note>
<note n="0510004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0510004">清淨施十相；不留滯施 asakta-dāna, 不執取施 parāmṛṣṭa-, 不積聚施 asambhṛta-, 不高舉施 nunnata-, 無所依施 anrśrit-, 不退弱施 alīna-, 不下劣施 adīna-, 不向背施 avimukha-, 不望報恩施 pratīkāranapekṣa-, 不希異熟 vipākarapekṣa-.</note>
<note n="0510005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0510005">不＝無【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0510006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0510006">〔世〕－【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0510007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0510007">令＝今【元】</note>
<note n="0510008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0510008">畜＝蓄【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0510009" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0510009">嚮＝響【三】【宮】</note>
</p>
